viewData.name: ASUS 15.6" UX533FD Laptop
viewData.short_description: Buy ASUS 15.6" UX533FD Laptop featuring 1.8 GHz Intel Core i7-8565U Quad-Core, 16GB DDR4 | 512GB NVMe M.2 SSD 15.6" 1920 x 1080 Display. Review ASUS
viewData.long_description: The 15.6" UX533FD Laptop from Asus features a 15.6" display with a 1920 x 1080 Full HD resolution for crisp, clear viewing. Specs-wise, it's powered by a 1.8 GHz Intel Core i7-8565U quad-core processor, 16GB of DDR4 RAM, an NVIDIA GeForce GTX 1050 graphics card, and a 512GB NVMe M.2 SSD. With these combined, this system can tackle everyday tasks such as browsing the internet, composing and editing documents, streaming online videos, and even gaming. Additionally, an NVMe SSD enables this system to boot and load applications quickly. Other integrated features include an SD media card reader, 802.11ac Wi-Fi, Bluetooth 5.0, USB Type-A and Type-C ports, an HDMI port, a webcam, and a 3.5mm combo audio jack. The operating system installed is Windows 10 Home (64-Bit).
